videos.description: Nathan Rourke fakes the toss to A.J. Oulette and runs it in himself for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Ohio's Rourke runs in first score

videos.description: Billy Bahl attempts a pass over the middle and is intercepted by Javan Hagan.
videos.headline: Ohio's defense creates an interception

videos.description: After throwing an interception, Billy Bahl comes right back and finds James Gardner for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Miami (OH) QB rebounds from pick with TD

videos.description: Miami (OH)'s Alonzo Smith is met by a boatload of defenders but keeps his legs churning to score a 16-yard touchdown to tie the game at 14.
videos.headline: Redhawks tie game with crazy TD

videos.description: Billy Bahl attempts a pass to his receiver but Jalen Fox intercepts it and returns it 25 yards to the 4-yard line.
videos.headline: Redhawks' Bahl throws second pick

videos.description: Bobcats' Rourke takes the QB keeper and runs for a 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bobcats' Rourke second TD gives them lead

videos.description: Nathan Rourke delivers a back-shoulder throw to WR Papi White for a 14-yard touchdown. This would make the score 28-14.
videos.headline: Ohio extends lead with TD

videos.description: Billy Bahl throws a fade route to James Gardner for a Miami (Ohio) 3-yard touchdown, making the score 28-21.
videos.headline: RedHawks TD cuts into lead before half

videos.description: Billy Bahl throws it up to James Gardner  and he leaps to make a nice 25-yard touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Miami (OH) tight end Gardner scores third TD

videos.description: Nathan Rourke finds Jerrid Marhefka for an 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bobcats' Rourke throws third TD

videos.description: Nathan Rourke calls his own number and takes the QB keeper in for a 1-yard touchdown. He has accounted for all six scores.
videos.headline: Bobcats' Rourke scores again, has accounted for all six TD's

videos.description: Billy Bahl completes the pass to Jared Murphy for four yards but gets suplexed by Chad Moore before he can get a first down.
videos.headline: Ohio defender uses wrestling move to stop Miami (OH) on 4th down
